---
import storyImage from "../assets/story-girl.png";
---

<section class="overflow-hidden bg-[#FAF7F2] py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-14 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:gap-16">
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src={storyImage.src}
          alt="A young girl smiling with quiet confidence"
          class="h-[460px] w-full rounded-[2rem] object-cover sm:h-[620px] lg:rounded-[3rem]"
        />
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#D97706] sm:text-sm">
          A Child's Story
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1F2937] sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl">
          &ldquo;Someone believed in me before I believed in myself.&rdquo;
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-[#1F2937]/70 md:text-xl">
          With steady learning support and mentorship, Priya found the confidence to read aloud, ask questions and dream bigger.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-8 font-semibold text-[#1F2937]">
          &mdash; Priya, Student
        </p>

        <a
          href="/stories"
          class="mt-10 inline-block font-semibold text-[#D97706] transition hover:text-[#1F2937]"
        >
          Read More Stories &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
